ICSIL Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for 48 Data Entry Operator Posts
Prasanna / All Government Jobs / Aug 29, 2025, 15:22 IST
 Intelligent Communication Systems India Limited
 48 Jobs |  Posted On : 29-Aug-2025 |  Delhi |  Salary : 22,411 to 22,411




FOLLOW

Intelligent Communication Systems India Limited (ICSIL) has declared the official notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for 48 Data Entry Operator Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the Intermediate (10+2) can grab this chance and apply for these posts. Here we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for the ICSIL Recruitment 2025. Interested and eligible candidates can apply on or before the last date of application.




If you are looking for more, here is a list of Government Jobs in 2025 that you can all apply for. Use this link for more jobs in Delhi.

ICSIL Recruitment 2025 - Eligibility Criteria
Name of the Posts	No.of Vacancies	Qualification
Data Entry Operator 	48	Intermediate (10+2)

Age Limit for the ICSIL Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Age Limit: 18 years.

Selection Process for the ICSIL Recruitment 2025

Intervew

Salary Structure for the ICSIL Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Salary: Rs. 22,411 /- per month.

Application fee for the ICSIL Recruitment 2025

For All Candidates: Rs. 590/-
How to Apply for the ICSIL Recruitment 2025
Visit the official website.
Go to the recruitment or career page.
Check for the Data Entry Operator notification 2025.
Read the notification carefully.
Check the eligibility criteria.
If you meet the eligibility criteria.
Click on the Apply Online link.
Log in with your email ID and Password.
Fill out the given details carefully.
Pay the application fee.
Submit the application form and take a printout of the application form for further reference.

Important Dates

Starting Date of Application	01-09-2025
Last Date of Application	04-09-2025
